Alliance Trust CEO Garrett-Cox to Meet Activists, Telegraph Says

-- B y   L a r s   P a u l s s o n
-- 
2011-04-17T08:18:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/alliance-trust-ceo-garrett-cox-to-meet-activists-telegraph-says.html
Alliance Trust Plc (ATST)  Chief Executive
Officer Katherine Garrett-Cox will meet with activist investors
Laxey Partners Ltd. and Elliott International as she seeks
support of her business plan, the  Sunday Telegraph  said.  Garrett-Cox will meet the shareholders ahead of next
month’s annual general meeting after Laxey criticized the U.K.-
based company’s performance, she told the newspaper in an
interview. Shareholder returns rose 19 percent and the dividend
accelerated to 3 percent growth, Garrett-Cox said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lars Paulsson in London at 
 lpaulsson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  